title: [Proposal] Distribute RNBW rewards to community
body:
HaloDAO (HALO) has seen strong user adoption from its inception to its launching. The team is rewarding community participation with RNBW tokens.

In line with this, HaloDAO team will be distributing 35000 RNBW tokens to the most active community members. The said distribution will take place on July 14, 2021.

The goal is to vote for this proposal to begin incentives.
author: 0x30Ca8F1e13978a7A819af012665CFa7E49F1c554
